io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog

Interface PrologMap

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<PrologTerm>, Iterable<PrologTerm>, Map<PrologTerm,PrologTerm>, PrologElement, PrologList, PrologTerm

    public interface PrologMap
extends PrologList, Map<PrologTerm,PrologTerm>
    A PrologTerm that maps PrologTerm keys to PrologTerm values. A map cannot contain duplicate keys. Each key can map to at most one value.
    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain
